data.description: Check out this charming 3 bedroom home with a large fenced in backyard, detached 2 car garage with extra storage and so much more! Large eat in kitchen and a den with a wood burning fireplace. 42x10 enclosed back porch area with offers endless possibilities! Walking distance to parks. Contact your favorite realtor today because this gem will be gone tomorrow! Before making an offer Buyer and/or buyer agent should verify all MLS data.
